Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 那么早出门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跑下步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拳击这种运动 如果比赛后就松懈下来\N很容易退步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫中本，和弟弟龙平是没有血缘关系的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自前年父母因事故身亡之后，二人就一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是认真耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦，早上就在唸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟以前虽然有参加黑道，常让父母头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在一边打工 一边打拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去年以新人之姿过关斩将，即将要挑战日本冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-那我出门了.   -路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大学生，因有父母的保险金和留下的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有很积极投入求职活动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,(拳击手的姐姐)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了，时间不早了，该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,中本小姐, 要去上课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想说你们姐弟独自生活 应该会很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要的话可以找我商量 像是钱方面等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然楼下单身的田岛先生嘴里说要帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但眼睛一直盯着我身体看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我赶时间, 先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗好澡了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那换我洗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有公司要录取你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你嘴碎，迟早会被录取的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果下次比赛我获胜的话，用奖金去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,相反地?你要赢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在之前我发现到了龙平\N有把我当作一般女性来看待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这样看他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,龙平, 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有, 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一下子有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-请住手   -反正你没事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-有什么关系啦.   -要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就说请你住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想干嘛啊？   -什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？想打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-想讨打啊.   -龙平，不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-不然要怎样？   -龙平，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,会长，这事要怎么解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子有反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可否请你撤销告诉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为龙平把他打到住院 演变成致人受伤事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我家小孩住院了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天去看他，脸部很肿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不知该如何说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,龙平是我们拳击队的明日之星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请你原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,才不管他是什么星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,会对平常人出手重击的拳击手\N他头脑是否有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你要留这种人做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,会长，这种人要留他干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-无耻的是你儿子吧.   -等等，龙平不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他骚扰女生而且毛手毛脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家伙完全没反省耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这种人应该要被抓去关的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-等着瞧吧   -不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,龙平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,中本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友听说被住在这里的拳击手殴打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会是龙平打的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真没想到是龙平打的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过拳击手如对一般人出手，则无法参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那个被打的小孩父亲的关系匪浅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我向他拜讬的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,或许就会撤销伤害控诉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是轻而易举的事，中本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,取而代之的就是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以和有男女生交往关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的啊，都读到大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不用出赛了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的话就没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟的事要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他是否还能当拳击手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？当我的情人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了，但我弟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天晚上10点过来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是会长村田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才他父亲来电说要撤销伤害控诉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说是你认识的朋友帮忙劝说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事不用再说了，进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-请住手   -为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,撤销伤害控诉后就反悔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是过分的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道你弟弟是否还能当拳击手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,撤销诉讼了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是可以再提起诉讼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的立场该放哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要再提起伤害控诉也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子也没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不该做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事是很愉快的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是你才有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-在说什么啊？   -好好去思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事应该懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的胸部，让我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要~不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,果然就如我想的一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好棒的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-有感觉啊.   -放开, 才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,房间就只有我们二人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,变怎样不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的话对你比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不然让你活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也抵抗不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么罩杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么罩杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒，晃来晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要乖喔，美人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,脱下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,胸罩好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,装了这个奶子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么罩杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有感觉   -那这边有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,奶头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,奶子爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说爽不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-在床上了哦   -会痛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,痛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会痛, 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是想了很久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才说过这房里只有我们二人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,新东宝翻译\N（98堂 Yamete 提取）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这奶子真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不想痛的话 手就乖乖这样摆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这奶子真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这里敏感度如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴会有多爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了, 看到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没毛啊, 真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,发出淫荡叫声了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.09,0:24:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,张开来看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.69,0:25:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.04,0:26:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.85,0:26:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还没碰到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.72,0:26:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.07,0:27:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这种焦急的感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.81,0:27:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要碰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.08,0:27:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.56,0:27:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.16,0:27:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.57,0:27:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.38,0:27:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我都还没怎么弄耶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.81,0:28:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要张开
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.17,0:28:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.44,0:28:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再让你爽一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.62,0:29:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.26,0:30:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再张大一点给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.00,0:30:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿淋淋了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.34,0:30:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,湿成这样子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.41,0:30:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.35,0:30:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这里，有看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.49,0:30:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.36,0:30:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手指来插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.25,0:31:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想插进去对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.32,0:31:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股好好挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,翘高
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,张开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.82,0:31:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-想插入吗？   -想
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.09,0:32:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,说请用力插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.82,0:32:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请用力插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.49,0:32:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你真变态耶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股好明显
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.03,0:32:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.84,0:32:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿了 很容易插入
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.75,0:33:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.89,0:33:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来搅动看看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.77,0:33:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,屁眼好明显
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脚再张开来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.34,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.01,0:34:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.75,0:34:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,同时弄阴核哪种较爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.22,0:34:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种较爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-不用拜讬我吗？   -拜讬你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.90,0:34:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.90,0:34:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.74,0:35:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.29,0:35:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.23,0:35:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.03,0:35:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.94,0:36:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,手指来弄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.35,0:36:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.73,0:37:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了…要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.44,0:37:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,湿淋淋的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.58,0:37:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.26,0:38:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.40,0:38:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喷这么多淫水, 真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.38,0:39:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,向那边舔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.99,0:39:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.74,0:40:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吗？开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.35,0:40:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.62,0:40:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.55,0:40:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,难受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.25,0:41:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对, 含深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.02,0:41:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,顶到喉咙了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.77,0:42:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来插了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.31,0:42:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.85,0:42:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来中间一点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.93,0:42:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,戴保险套
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.14,0:42:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-戴保险套   -有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.21,0:42:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.15,0:43:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-直接插就好.   -不要, 戴保险套
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.35,0:43:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.63,0:43:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上套子了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.16,0:43:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.86,0:43:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.47,0:43:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,插了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.75,0:44:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.55,0:44:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.00,0:45:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴进进出出看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.35,0:45:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡的姿势，看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.21,0:46:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.08,0:46:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快要去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.63,0:46:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.50,0:46:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快要去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.07,0:47:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,搞一下阴核
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.01,0:47:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.62,0:47:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,用力插哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.82,0:47:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.43,0:47:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这么爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.04,0:47:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被插的很爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.65,0:48:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,被打会爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.73,0:48:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.47,0:48:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.89,0:48:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么会去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.97,0:49:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.99,0:49:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.35,0:49:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,插得真爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.50,0:51:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行, 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.46,0:51:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.46,0:51:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,张开一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.40,0:51:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡的姿势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.21,0:51:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去摸看看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.82,0:52:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再去摸
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.16,0:52:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被插得很爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.20,0:52:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.27,0:52:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.15,0:53:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.89,0:53:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.50,0:53:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.03,0:53:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爽到要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.43,0:54:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.63,0:54:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.53,0:54:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.87,0:55:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.02,0:55:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.30,0:55:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,套子破了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.38,0:55:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 破掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.93,0:56:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你真有性魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.00,0:56:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,再来做一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.35,0:56:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,接着就不戴套子来插了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再来爽一次，屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.62,0:56:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.30,0:56:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不听话 你弟弟就没办法打拳击喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.64,0:56:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.78,0:56:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来插了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.05,0:57:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴没戴套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.69,0:57:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面插真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.36,0:57:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,后面插很爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.33,0:58:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大奶子真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.26,0:59:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.21,0:59:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股也晃动的??真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.62,0:59:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.92,1:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒, 插好深啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.52,1:00:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,用力插哦, 好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.79,1:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.87,1:00:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怀孕吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.50,1:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.77,1:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-要去了   -给我生孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.04,1:01:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-不行，抽出来   -少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.64,1:01:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.98,1:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要   -下种了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.45,1:01:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下种成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.19,1:01:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拜讬抽出来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.99,1:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.67,1:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.44,1:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自被他射里面之后\N肉体似乎渐渐迎合田岛先生的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.29,1:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,每晚田岛先生都来搞我的肉体
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.09,1:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,于是终于演变成性淫乱的关系
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.73,1:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我察觉到我已经回不去以前龙平喜欢的那个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.69,1:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,腰用力动
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.37,1:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动一动
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.73,1:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,趴前面一点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.73,1:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看屁眼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.83,1:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.37,1:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.13,1:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以后再继续搞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.90,1:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有穿来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.63,1:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.50,1:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.12,1:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快点脱
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.68,1:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.83,1:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好好让我看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.05,1:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的视野啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.86,1:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.00,1:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,奶头都跑出来了耶
