Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.96,1:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.90,1:11:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.99,1:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.93,1:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的鸡巴已经好好品尝过了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.80,1:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再过一下她就不会抗拒了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.94,1:11:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙好了
